# Ex 0 — Preparação inicial

### criar o imposter
POST http://localhost:2525/imposters
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "port": 3000,
  "protocol": "http"
}

### ver se foi criado
GET http://localhost:2525/imposters/3000

### testar que da 404 sem stubs
GET http://localhost:3000/qualquer-coisa

#-----------------------------------------------------

# Ex 1 - stub lista de marcas

### apagar e recriar
DELETE http://localhost:2525/imposters/3000

### criar imposter com stub das marcas
POST http://localhost:2525/imposters
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "port": 3000,
  "protocol": "http",
  "stubs": [
    {
      "predicates": [
        {"equals": {"method": "GET", "path": "/api/marcas"}}
      ],
      "responses": [
        {"is": {"statusCode": 200, "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}, "body": {"marcas": ["Toyota", "Audi", "Ford", "Volvo", "Honda"]}}}
      ]
    }
  ]
}

### testar
GET http://localhost:3000/api/marcas

#-----------------------------------------------------

# Ex 2 - stub pesquisa de carros por marca

### apagar e recriar
DELETE http://localhost:2525/imposters/3000

### criar imposter com stubs ex1 + ex2
POST http://localhost:2525/imposters
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "port": 3000,
  "protocol": "http",
  "stubs": [
    {
      "predicates": [
        {"equals": {"method": "GET", "path": "/api/marcas"}}
      ],
      "responses": [
        {"is": {"statusCode": 200, "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}, "body": {"marcas": ["Toyota", "Audi", "Ford", "Volvo", "Honda"]}}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "predicates": [
        {"equals": {"method": "GET", "path": "/api/cars", "query": {"brand": "Toyota"}}}
      ],
      "responses": [
        {"is": {"statusCode": 200, "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}, "body": {"brand": "Toyota", "results": [{"id": 1, "modelo": "Corolla", "preco": 25000}, {"id": 2, "modelo": "Yaris", "preco": 18000}]}}}
      ]
    }
  ]
}

### testar com brand=Toyota
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cars?brand=Toyota

### teste negativo sem query
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cars

