### testar sem query
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cars

### confirmar que ex2 ainda funciona
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cars?brand=Toyota

#-----------------------------------------------------

# Ex 4 - login bem sucedido

### apagar e recriar
DELETE http://localhost:2525/imposters/3000

### criar imposter com stubs ex1 ao ex4
POST http://localhost:2525/imposters
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "port": 3000,
  "protocol": "http",
  "stubs": [
    {
      "predicates": [
        {"equals": {"method": "GET", "path": "/api/marcas"}}
      ],
      "responses": [
        {"is": {"statusCode": 200, "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}, "body": {"marcas": ["Toyota", "Audi", "Ford", "Volvo", "Honda"]}}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "predicates": [
        {"equals": {"method": "GET", "path": "/api/cars", "query": {"brand": "Toyota"}}}
      ],
      "responses": [
        {"is": {"statusCode": 200, "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}, "body": {"brand": "Toyota", "results": [{"id": 1, "modelo": "Corolla", "preco": 25000}, {"id": 2, "modelo": "Yaris", "preco": 18000}]}}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "predicates": [
        {"equals": {"method": "GET", "path": "/api/cars"}}
      ],
      "responses": [
        {"is": {"statusCode": 200, "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}, "body": {"results": []}}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "predicates": [
        {"equals": {"method": "POST", "path": "/api/login", "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}}},
        {"deepEquals": {"body": {"username": "admin", "password": "secret"}}}
      ],
      "responses": [
        {"is": {"statusCode": 200, "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}, "body": {"status": "ok", "token": "validtoken"}}}
      ]
    }
  ]
}

### testar login correcto
POST http://localhost:3000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "admin", "password": "secret"}

#-----------------------------------------------------

# Ex 5 - login com credenciais inválidas

### apagar e recriar
DELETE http://localhost:2525/imposters/3000

### criar imposter com stubs ex1 ao ex5
POST http://localhost:2525/imposters
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "port": 3000,
  "protocol": "http",
  "stubs": [
    {
      "predicates": [
        {"equals": {"method": "GET", "path": "/api/marcas"}}
      ],
      "responses": [
        {"is": {"statusCode": 200, "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}, "body": {"marcas": ["Toyota", "Audi", "Ford", "Volvo", "Honda"]}}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "predicates": [
        {"equals": {"method": "GET", "path": "/api/cars", "query": {"brand": "Toyota"}}}
      ],
      "responses": [
        {"is": {"statusCode": 200, "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}, "body": {"brand": "Toyota", "results": [{"id": 1, "modelo": "Corolla", "preco": 25000}, {"id": 2, "modelo": "Yaris", "preco": 18000}]}}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "predicates": [
        {"equals": {"method": "GET", "path": "/api/cars"}}
      ],
      "responses": [
        {"is": {"statusCode": 200, "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}, "body": {"results": []}}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "predicates": [
        {"equals": {"method": "POST", "path": "/api/login", "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}}},
        {"deepEquals": {"body": {"username": "admin", "password": "secret"}}}
      ],
      "responses": [
        {"is": {"statusCode": 200, "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}, "body": {"status": "ok", "token": "validtoken"}}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "predicates": [
        {"equals": {"method": "POST", "path": "/api/login"}}
      ],
      "responses": [
        {"is": {"statusCode": 401, "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}, "body": {"error": "invalid_credentials"}}}
      ]
    }
  ]
}

### testar login errado
POST http://localhost:3000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "hacker", "password": "1234"}

### confirmar que ex4 ainda funciona
POST http://localhost:3000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "admin", "password": "secret"}

